    ThemeSelect

    public abstract class ThemeSelectBase
extends javax.faces.component.UIInput
implements IThemeSelect, IceClientBehaviorHolder
    The themeSelect component can be used to dynamically change the current ACE ThemeRoller theme in the application.

    For more information, see the ThemeSelect Wiki Documentation.
